          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生荀攸，字公达，曾拜黄门侍郎。一向弃官在家，今闻曹将军招贤纳士，故\n同叔父来投，烦劳通报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位请少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军甲进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启将军：外面有颖川荀彧、荀攸叔侄二人，来投麾下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾闻此二人大名久矣，快快请来相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军甲出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请二位先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（荀彧、荀攸随中军甲同进门见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧、荀攸",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军在上，愚叔侄参见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消，只行常礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧、荀攸",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文若乃王佐之才，公达亦海内名士。今日来投，想必有以教我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔者高祖东伐，为义帝缟素，而天下归心。今天子播越，将军可乘此时奉主，\n以从民望，大顺也；秉至公以服豪杰，大略也；扶宏义以致英俊，大德也。天\n下虽有逆节，必不能为患矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙哇！文若真吾之子房也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾自知浅陋，不足采听。有乡人郭嘉，字奉孝；兖州程昱、字仲德，皆当今贤\n士，敢荐于麾下。我已有书约彼，想早晚即到也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此二人吾已闻名久矣。若得来归，皆公之力也。今屈文若为行军司马，公达为\n行军校尉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧、荀攸",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四勇士引于禁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生成熊腰与猿臂，\n虎视眈眈相貌奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是辕门。\n有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，壮士何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃泰山巨平人氏，姓于名禁，带领健壮数百，来投曹将军的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军甲进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启将军：有泰山巨平人于禁领众来投。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着他们进来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军甲出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军有令，教你们进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（于禁、四勇士随中军甲同进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军在上，于禁率众叩见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等来投帐下，有何本领？"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼学成穿杨技，\n一箭双雕不足奇。\n猛勇争先破强敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "斩将冲锋凭武艺、曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等就将手中兵器比试一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（于禁舞枪，四勇士同舞双刀，同舞毕。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙啊！果然武艺高强。命汝为点军司马，各勇士随营差遣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程昱、郭嘉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一诺千金重知己，"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭嘉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大展经纶献珠玑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱、郭嘉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是。\n有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军甲出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱、郭嘉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烦劳通报：程昱、郭嘉投见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军甲进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启将军：院门外有程昱、郭嘉二人投见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，公达为我迎接。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀攸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（荀攸出迎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀攸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二兄来了。小弟已作先容，将军盼望久矣。就请相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（荀攸引程昱、郭嘉同见曹操。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱、郭嘉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军在上，程昱、郭嘉参加！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。久仰令名，殊深渴想；今蒙不弃，大慰平生。暂为军中从事，另日表荐\n便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱、郭嘉",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夏侯惇、典韦同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "枪刀林中敌万军，开疆展土夏侯惇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双提铁戟扬天下，勇猛当先岂让人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏侯惇打躬！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夏侯惇唤典韦进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过来，叩见将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军在上，小将叩见！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（典韦行礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此系何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乃陈留人，姓典名韦。旧随张邈，与帐下人不和，手杀数十人，逃窜山中。\n我因出猎，见他赶逐猛虎过溪，收在军中。今特荐于帐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我观此人，相貌魁梧，必非凡品。有何本领，你可讲来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军问我有何艺，\n细听典韦说端的：\n力过凡流勇莫敌。\n军中斩将敢夺旗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "生成雄壮真奇异、手中惯使双铁戟、曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，可把双戟试舞一回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（典韦舞双戟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双戟舞动寒光起，\n凛凛威风世间稀。\n电掣风翻似雪飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖风声〗。帅字旗被刮倒。四将官同趋扶，扶不住，各喧噪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "将官甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启将军：大风陡起，帅字旗将要刮倒，众军士拥护不住。"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪开了，俺来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霎时一阵狂风起，\n卷起尘沙双目迷。\n满营人惊马乱嘶。\n扶住中军帅字旗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（典韦扶帅字旗绕场，归中举定。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "风止了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（典韦仍立旗于左台口。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃古之恶来也！\n夏侯惇，取锦袍一件过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夏侯惇取锦袍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "锦袍在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "典韦，赐汝锦袍一袭，命汝为帐前都尉，今后不可离我左右！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（典韦接袍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "典韦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勇如孟贲真奇力，捷如庆忌似鸟飞。扫荡贼寇全仗你，护卫中军莫远离。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊文若，想我父亲自陈留避难，隐居琅琊。汝可为我修书一封，即遣泰山太守\n应劭接取，护送到来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操下座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我父琅琊把祸避，\n即去接取莫要迟。\n盼望严亲早回归。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖尾声〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "曹操→中军甲",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "中军甲→曹操",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "中军甲→荀彧",
